## Data Flow Diagrams

### Upload Flow
```
User picks PDF
  ‚Üí InputBar attach button
  ‚Üí file.api.js POST /api/files/upload (FormData)
  ‚Üí upload.middleware (multer, validates PDF ‚â§10MB)
  ‚Üí file.controller
  ‚Üí pdf.service (extract text)
  ‚Üí chunker.service (split into 800-char chunks w/ overlap)
  ‚Üí embedding.service (Mistral batch embed all chunks)
  ‚Üí pinecone.service (upsert vectors with metadata)
  ‚Üí response: { fileId, fileName, chunkCount }
  ‚Üí frontend stores fileId in local state
  ‚Üí FileUploadBadge shows "Ready to chat with file"
```

### Query Flow
```
User sends message
  ‚Üí chat.controller.sendMessage receives { message, chatId, fileId? }
  ‚Üí If fileId present:
      ‚Üí classifier.service: is query file-related?
      ‚Üí If YES:
          ‚Üí embed query (Mistral)
          ‚Üí pinecone.service.queryChunks (filtered by fileId + userId)
          ‚Üí build grounded prompt with top chunks
          ‚Üí generateRagResponse via Gemini
      ‚Üí If NO:
          ‚Üí falls through to normal generateResponse()
  ‚Üí Either path: save message, save aiMessage, return response
```

